# Fixed-size Images

When adding small logo/images on summit pages (for example under `## Date and venue`), prefer the `image-size` shortcode over manual HTML.

Rules:

- Use `{{< image-size src="..." alt="..." width="..." height="..." >}}`
- If the image must be clickable, add `href="..."`:
  - `{{< image-size src="..." href="..." alt="..." width="200" height="200" >}}`

Avoid:
- Manual raw `<img>` / `<a>` wrapping for summit logo images (use the shortcode instead).
